channel.title: Cache keeps on getting damaged? help?
channel.description:
How odd. Every time that I [b]close my client[/b] somehow the cache "main_file_cache_BLAH" gets corrupted or overwritten, as when I log back in after opening my client, I see the GWD stuff in place of grass, fences, etc. I know this can be fixed with a new cache - I just have to replace it every time after I close the client.
Any ideas why it does this?
